gpt-5-2025-08-07.solvingStrategy:
DSL:
- detectBlocks(color): find all 3x3 regions of a single nonzero color
- keepFives(): in output, copy all cells equal to 5 from input
- preserveBlocks(blocks): for each 3x3 uniform block in blocks, copy its cells to output; if a cell inside the 3x3 is not the block color, replace it with the paired block color (if any); otherwise keep as block color
- zeroElse(): set all other non-5, non-block cells to 0
Algorithm:
1) init output as zeros
2) keepFives()
3) B = detectBlocks(any color)
4) if |B|>=1: preserveBlocks(B)
5) zeroElse()
